[b]702
Profile:[/b]
Originally a quartet, 702 cosisted of sisters Irish, Orish and LeMisha Grinstead and their cousin Amelia Childs. In 1994 Amelia left the group and was replaced by Kameelah Williams. Orish left the group soon after. In 2001, Kameelah left to pursue a solo career and was briefly replaced by Cree Lamore until she returned to the group in 2003. Kameelah again left the group and was replaced by Orish. Orish Grinstead died on April 20, 2008, at the age of 27 from kidney failure.
